              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/6734</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/6734</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<h2>My learning journal</h2>
<h3><a title="week 9 plenary - close" href="http://www.olds.ac.uk/the-course/week-9-plenary-close">Week Nine - Showcase</a></h3>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->Review and comment on showcased projects</p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->Go back and fill in previous weeks work</p>
<h3><a title="week 8 reflect" href="http://www.olds.ac.uk/the-course/week-8-reflect">Week Eight - Reflect</a></h3>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->Created <a title="ARTiFactors design narrative reflection" href="http://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/8152">My Design Narrative</a></p>
<p style="cursor:auto"><!--NO CSS-->Commented on others' design naratives</p>
<h3><a title="week 7 evaluate" href="http://www.olds.ac.uk/the-course/week-7-evaluate">Week Seven - Evaluate</a></h3>
