              <title>In search for the integration of Learning Design (LD) and Teacher Inquiry into student learning (TISL)</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/6603</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/6603</guid>
