<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Scanlon, Conole, Littleton, Kerawalla, Gaved, Twiner, Collins, Mulholland, 2009. Personal inquiry (PI) Innovations in participatory design and models for inquiry learning.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>K&ouml;nings, Brand-Gruwel and van Merri&euml;nboer, 2011. Participatory instructional redesign by students and teachers in secondary education: effects on perceptions of instruction</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
