<p>Wieman, C. (2004), &lsquo;Professors who are scholars: bringing the act of discovery to the classroom&rsquo;, presentation at The Reinvention Center Conference, November, 2004. <a href="http://www.reinventioncenter.miami.edu/conference_05/wieman/presentation.htm"><em>Integrating Research into Undergraduate Education: The Value Added</em></a>.</p>
