<p>Trausan-Matu, S., Dascalu, M., &amp; Dessus, P. (2012). Considering textual complexity and comprehension in Computer-Supported Collaborative Learning. In S. A. Cerri, W. J. Clancey, G. Papadourakis &amp; K. Panourgia (Eds.), <em>11th Int. Conf. on Intelligent Tutoring Systems (ITS 2012)</em> (pp. 352&ndash;357). New York: Springer.</p>
<p>van Es, R., &amp; Koper, R. (2006). Testing the pedagogical expressiveness of IMS LD. <em>Educ. Technol. &amp; Soc., 9</em>(1), 229&ndash;249.</p>
<p>Wenger, E. (1998). <em>Communities of practice</em>. Cambridge: Cambridge University Press.</p>
<p>Wilson, S. (2008). Patterns of Personal Learning Environments. <em>Interact. Learn. Envir.</em>, 16, 17&ndash;34.</p>]]></description>
