                    <item>
              <title>Pattern: Pyramid</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/6015</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/6015</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>The <a href="http://www.slideshare.net/yandim/the-pyramid-pedagogical-pattern-and-a-sample-associated-educational-scenario">Pyramid pedagogical pattern</a> is presented together with a sample pedagogical scenario.</p>
<p>An alternative educational scenario based on the Pyramid pattern is also included, that was proposed by a university professor in another workshop. This scenario is provided in its <a href="http://www.slideshare.net/yandim/scenario-boeb2011-20111130">original version</a> and in a<a href="http://www.slideshare.net/yandim/alternative-pyramidbased-scenario-simplified-version"> simplified version.</a></p>]]></description>
