                    <item>
              <title>LessonLAMS</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/5779</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/5779</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>LessonLAMS is a new hosted version of LAMS that allows educators to</p>
<ul>
<li>Preview Learning Designs (ie, view as a learner)</li>
<li>Open/view/edit Learning Designs as an author, including a new simplified one page editor</li>
<li>Run Learning Designs with student groups of up to 30 students (using a URL + login code, or teacher-managed student accounts).</li>
</ul>
<p>A related feature to LessonLAMS is the new "Embed" feature, which allows a LAMS sequence which has been shared through the LAMS Community (http://www.lamscommunity.org/ ) to be "embedded" into a webpage (eg, blog). The embedded design can then be openned directly into LessonLAMS to allow for rapid editing or launching with students. For an example of a blog with embedded sequences, see http://jamesdalziel.blogspot.com/</p>
