              <description><![CDATA[<p>The 2011 Pedagogic Planner meeting will be held in Oxford, UK on Thursday, 29th September.&nbsp; It is a forum for the discussion of issues in Learning Design and Pedagogic Planners. The original concept of these meetings was to bring together Learning Design experts from around the world to explore the concept of pedagogic planners, compare and contrast existing work in this field, and attempt to define future directions for research and implementation. &nbsp;James Dalziel will be facilitating the meeting together with Diana Laurillard and Liz Masterman.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
