              <description><![CDATA[<p>In an attempt to use some of my newfound H800 learning I am attempting to make a change to my existing traditional (read boring) lessons to ones which involve the use of a wiki.&nbsp; Based on an idea by a fellow H800er I&rsquo;ve produced a compendium design which I submit to the Cloudworks community for full destructive testing. &nbsp;<br />The activity asks work placement students to each bring an issue/problem (which they are comfortable with) to the wiki, select one for discussion, identify the best solution and then possibly implement solution/practice back to workplace.</p>
